               <chronitemset>
                  <event>Moved to Berkeley, California, joined First Congregational Church; served church in Antioch, California; had interim pastorates and speaking engagements throughout Bay area. Was instrumental in organization of South Berkeley Community Church, first integrated church in Berkeley.</event>
